# OBI-WAN KPI Framework

| KPI | Why It Matters | Formula / Measurement | Audience |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Pathway Clarification Rate | Measures whether OBI-WAN helps users move from vague intent to a concrete path | % of vague-intent sessions ending with a narrowed path | CEO, Product |
| Actionable Recommendation Rate | Measures whether the system produces usable next steps | % of sessions ending with at least one grounded recommendation | CEO, CTO |
| Helpfulness Score | Measures perceived user value | Avg. 1–5 helpfulness rating | CEO, Product |
| Time to Useful Answer | Measures interaction efficiency | Avg. turns to grounded answer | CEO, CTO |
| Hallucination-Free Recommendation Rate | Measures trustworthiness | % of sessions with no unsupported recommendations | CTO, CEO |
| Tool-Routing Reliability | Measures correct system behavior | % of prompts where tools were invoked appropriately | CTO |
